        <!-- help page content -->
        
        <h3 class="govuk-heading-l">How do I change the email address on my account?</h3>
        <p class="govuk-body">
            If you need to change or update the email address associated with your account, follow these steps:
        </p>
        <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
            <li>Go to 'profile'.</li>
            <li>Select 'change my email address' from the related actions.</li>
            <li>Enter your new email address.</li>
            <li>We'll send you an email to this address with a code.</li>
            <li>Enter the code into the box provided and confirm.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="govuk-body">
            The next time you sign in, you will need to use this email address. Your old email address will no longer be recognised.
        </p>

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Do I need a separate email address for each organisation?</h3>
        <p class="govuk-body">
            No. You can associate as many organisations to one email address as you like.
        </p>
        <p class="govuk-body">
            With DfE Sign-in, one account is all you need.
        </p>

